{"tid":2406741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金正恩無視《禁煙法》  觀看春節演出時煙不離手","createTime":"2021-02-13T12:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T17:56:56.000Z","uid":66271,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b3f6dbe72983ea3d231e25109b9188db175c06","tid":2406741,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.yna.co.kr/photo/yna/YH/2021/02/12/PYH2021021202120004200_P4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.yna.co.kr%2Fphoto%2Fyna%2FYH%2F2021%2F02%2F12%2FPYH2021021202120004200_P4.jpg&h=c3084c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓聯社首爾2月12日電据朝中社12日報導，朝鮮國務委員會委員長金正恩11日在勞動黨第八屆中央委員會第二次全體會議閉幕後，同黨中央領導機構成員一起觀看了春節演出。<br />\n<br />\n在報導畫面中，金正恩觀看演出時煙不離手。朝鮮去年實施《禁煙法》，規定在影院等公共場所、兒童保育機構、教育機構、醫療和衛生設施、商業和服務設施、公共交通工具內指定禁煙區，違反吸煙秩序時予以處罰。"},{"pid":"36fa5b22782d177e8f8cbbebab30e7fb3a699b1a","tid":2406741,"uid":191926,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T12:59:48.000Z","msg":"邊個敢執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e171f2e0ff81dd2abae945369d29e26d3396504b","tid":2406741,"uid":77196,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"帝制之下，不嬲都係皇帝制律法俾賤民守，而皇帝自己根本唔需要守；鄰國都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2763365117697e6bbe08b4875d4db47ff0eb0d22","tid":2406741,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"耶穌在安息日作工"},{"pid":"e26fd53cfa0c55d855d53f00b6de7a56e65a1e9f","tid":2406741,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e171f2e0ff81dd2abae945369d29e26d3396504b","tid":2406741,"uid":77196,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:01:38.000Z","msg":"帝制之下，不嬲都係皇帝制律法俾賤民守，而皇帝自己根本唔需要守；鄰國都係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/